9
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:04,440
Po tom, čo ste hľadali drevo Mu Rong.

10
00:02:05,020 --> 00:02:06,839
Odvtedy si nič nepamätám.

11
00:02:08,580 --> 00:02:10,640
